name: ivna

# [ivna](https://github.com/VitthalS/ivna)
Intentionally Vulnerable Nodejs Application

Vulnerable Task Manager Application & APIs build using Nodejs, mongoose.

Made with ![Love](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/4301109/16754758/82e3a63c-4813-11e6-9430-6015d98aeaab.png) in India

The application contains the following vulnerabilities

- [x] XSS
- [x] Command Injection
- [x] URL Redirection
- [x] API Legacy Version Deprecation
- [x] BOLA (IDOR)
- [x] Common JWT Secret
- [x] Excessive Data exposure
- [x] Broken User Authentication
- [x] Exposed Database
